#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.36"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.36:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.36:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga "
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.36:0.3"
msgid "36. Pāṇasutta "
msgstr "36. Living Creatures "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.36:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso yaṃ imasmiṃ jambudīpe tiṇakaṭṭhasākhāpalāsaṃ tacchetvā ekajjhaṃ saṃhareyya; "
msgstr "Suppose a person was to strip all the grass, sticks, branches, and leaves in India, gather them together into one pile, "

msgctxt "sn56.36:1.2"
msgid "ekajjhaṃ saṃharitvā sūlaṃ kareyya. "
msgstr "and make them into stakes. "

msgctxt "sn56.36:1.3"
msgid "Sūlaṃ karitvā ye mahāsamudde mahantakā pāṇā te mahantakesu sūlesu āvuneyya, ye mahāsamudde majjhimakā pāṇā te majjhimakesu sūlesu āvuneyya, ye mahāsamudde sukhumakā pāṇā te sukhumakesu sūlesu āvuneyya. "
msgstr "Then they’d impale the large creatures in the ocean on large stakes; the medium-sized creatures on medium-sized stakes; and the small creatures on small stakes. "

msgctxt "sn56.36:1.4"
msgid "Apariyādinnā ca, bhikkhave, mahāsamudde oḷārikā pāṇā assu. "
msgstr "They wouldn’t run out of sizable creatures in the ocean before "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.442, sc2
msgctxt "sn56.36:2.1"
msgid "Atha imasmiṃ jambudīpe tiṇakaṭṭhasākhāpalāsaṃ parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya. "
msgstr "using up all the grass, sticks, branches, and leaves in India. "

msgctxt "sn56.36:2.2"
msgid "Ito bahutarā kho, bhikkhave, mahāsamudde sukhumakā pāṇā, ye na sukarā sūlesu āvunituṃ. "
msgstr "There are far more small creatures in the ocean than this, so it wouldn’t be feasible to impale them on stakes. "

msgctxt "sn56.36:2.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn56.36:2.4"
msgid "Sukhumattā, bhikkhave, attabhāvassa. "
msgstr "Because of the small size of those life-forms. "

msgctxt "sn56.36:2.5"
msgid "Evaṃ mahā kho, bhikkhave, apāyo. "
msgstr "That’s how big the plane of loss is. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.36:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ mahantasmā kho, bhikkhave, apāyasmā parimutto diṭṭhisampanno puggalo ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "A person accomplished in view, exempt from that vast plane of loss, truly understands: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.36:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.36:3.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
